edu.cscc.javaadventure

Class BasicObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.cscc.javaadventure.JAObject
      • edu.cscc.javaadventure.BasicObject

  • public class BasicObject
extends JAObject
    Represents a basic object in the JavaAdventure game. This class is just a wrapper for JAObject to make it easy to create new objects without needing to create a new class to extend the abstract class, and without needing to configure the setupDescriptionModifiers().

      • setupDescriptionModifiers

        protected void setupDescriptionModifiers()
        Abstract method used to configure the modifiers of an object based on object-specific rules. The implementation of this method should call JAObject.addDescriptionModifier(ModifierName, String), JAObject.clearDescriptionModifiers(), and JAObject.removeDescriptionModifier(ModifierName) to manage the modifiers.

        setupDescriptionModifiers in class JAObject
